hostel is based on / derived from OpenSandbox execd
(https://github.com/alibaba/opensandbox), also licensed under the Apache
License, Version 2.0. It started as a reimplementation of execd's OSEP-0013
isolated-execution model — bubblewrap namespace/overlay confinement, a
per-session upper-directory manager, a marker-framed long-running shell,
filesystem path confinement, and the files / directories / command / session
HTTP API surface — and is expected to diverge over time.

Per Apache-2.0 §4, any file that incorporates OpenSandbox source verbatim
retains the Apache-2.0 header together with OpenSandbox's copyright and
attribution notices.
